Usage: saveWhatIfTimingAssertions [-help] {-outfile <outfile> | -tclList } { <blackBoxCellName>}

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<blackBoxCellName>     # name of the blackbox or blackblob cell
                       # (string, optional)
-outfile <outfile>     # out file name (string, optional)
-tclList               # Generates the specifications as a Tcl list
                       # (bool, optional)